 941.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [692.7, 918.3, 711.5, 941.6]}, {"text": "15.75", "bbox": [755.2, 918.3, 813.3, 941.6]}, {"text": "43,562 $", "bbox": [892.7, 918.3, 992.1, 941.8]}, {"text": "13.33", "bbox": [1036.5, 918.3, 1094.6, 941.6]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2003 38,303,000 options were exercisable at an average exercise price of", "bbox": [168.8, 959.9, 1112.5, 983.2]}, {"text": "$12.97.  As of December 31, 2002, 37,461,000 options were exercisable at an average exercise price of", "bbox": [131.3, 983.9, 1112.5, 1007.2]}, {"text": "$11.92.", "bbox": [131.3, 1007.9, 206.7, 1031.2]}, {"text": "Employee Stock Purchase Plan", "bbox": [161.3, 1056.9, 483.3, 1080.2]}, {"text": "In April 1999, the Board of Directors approved the adoption of Juniper Networks 1999 Employee", "bbox": [168.8, 1105.8, 1112.4, 1129.1]}, {"text": "Stock Purchase Plan (the \"Purchase Plan\"). The Purchase Plan permits eligible employees to acquire", "bbox": [131.3, 1129.8, 1112.4, 1153.1]}, {"text": "shares of the Company's common stock through periodic payroll deductions of up to 10% of base", "bbox": [131.3, 1153.7, 1112.5, 1177.0]}, {"text": "compensation.  Each employee may purchase no more than 6,000 shares in any twelve-month period,", "bbox": [131.3, 1177.7, 1112.5, 1201.0]}, {"text": "and in no event, may an employee purchase more than $25,000 worth of stock, determined at the fair", "bbox": [131.3, 1201.7, 1112.5, 1225.0]}, {"text": "market value of the shares at the time such option is granted, in one calendar year.  The Purchase Plan is", "bbox": [131.3, 1225.6, 1112.6, 1248.9]}, {"text": "implemented in a series of offering periods, each six months in duration.  The price at which the common", "bbox": [131.3, 1249.6, 1112.5, 1272.9]}, {"text": "stock may be purchased is 85% of the lesser of the fair market value of the Company's common stock on", "bbox": [131.3, 1273.6, 1112.5, 1296.9]}, {"text": "the first day of the applicable offering period or on the last day of the respective offering period.", "bbox": [131.3, 1297.5, 1010.4, 1320.8]}, {"text": "During 2004, employees purchased 769,000 shares of common stock through the Purchase Plan at", "bbox": [168.8, 1344.5, 1112.6, 1367.8]}, {"text": "an average exercise price of $15.39 per share.  As of December 31, 2004, a total of 3,831,000 shares", "bbox": [131.3, 1368.4, 1112.5, 1391.7]}, {"text": "had been issued under the Purchase Plan at an average price of $7.95 per share, and 8,169,000 shares", "bbox": [131.3, 1392.4, 1112.5, 1415.7]}, {"text": "remained available for future issuance under the Purchase Plan.", "bbox": [131.3, 1416.4, 736.1, 1439.7]}]}